          "agency tension",
          "deterministic channel",
          "timeline branching",
          "island authority vs Dharma vs Jacob/Smokey"
        ],
        "notes": "Keep it roastable but kind\u2014frame the mechanics confusion as the show\u2019s chosen emotional fog, not \u201cgotcha\u201d writing."
